      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Xiaomi CL packs features that punch well above its price class. Here's what impressed me most:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Leica Camera Partnership",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Xiaomi 17T Pro and 17 Ultra feature cameras co-engineered with Leica. We're talking Leica Authentic and Leica Vibrant color profiles, 5x telephoto capability, and computational photography that handles low light beautifully. For a phone at this price point, the image quality is genuinely surprising.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "HyperOS Cross-Device Sync",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "HyperOS replaces MIUI and unifies the experience across phones, tablets, wearables, and smart home devices. Your fitness data, notifications, and smart home controls flow between devices without lag. It's the connective tissue that makes the ecosystem feel intentional rather than fragmented.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-Time Air Quality Monitoring",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Air Purifier 4 Compact doesn't just clean your air — it shows you exactly what's in it. PM2.5 levels, allergen counts, and VOC readings appear on the device and in the app. You can schedule purification around your routine or let it respond automatically to detected changes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "180Hz Mini LED Display",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
