            "text": "Xiaomi Mini LED Gaming Monitor G Pro 27i",
            "marks": [
              "l7"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " deserves special mention. 1152 dimming zones mean deep blacks and bright highlights simultaneously. The 180Hz refresh rate with 1ms response makes it competitive with monitors costing significantly more. If you game or do color-sensitive work, this display delivers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
