      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Xiaomi sells products directly through mi.com/us with US-based shipping and support. Product availability varies by category, but smartphones, wearables, monitors, and smart home devices are all accessible.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does Xiaomi CL compare to Samsung or Google ecosystems?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Xiaomi's strength is value. You get similar feature sets — health tracking, smart home control, cross-device sync — at lower price points. The ecosystem is less mature than Samsung's or Google's in terms of third-party integrations, but for pure Xiaomi-to-Xiaomi connectivity, it works remarkably well. Constant firmware updates keep closing the gap.",
            "marks": []
          }
